Get a specific assertion

getAssertion.Rd

Retrieve a specific assertion from the CIViC DB

getAssertion(id)

Arguments

id

Internal CIViC ID of the assertion of interest

Value

An S3 Object of type civic_api containing the content, url, and response

Examples

getAssertion(id = 1)
